Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boys, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans aren’t such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who needs tomorrow anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don’t hide your fists
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not old enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to sell your dreams away to uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boys, you’re the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who can pull the trigger in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re living in this senseless, ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,awesome world right at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t forget every truth or lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re way too young to die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this empty town lined with empty faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids took off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into this windless night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they want to change something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru's Shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way… What happened\Nto Iruka Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka’s scent ends right here…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\Nall we can do is search for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. Where’s Iruka Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…that Mizuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka Sensei…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That injury…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, this injury is nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m all right…\NI just had a little rush of pain…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody’s approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief\Nthe wound’s not deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere feels kind of heavy…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm…There must be something\Nbetween those two…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what I think is…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s up with the paw pad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Look carefully!\NThe little finger, the little finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little finger? Huh?!\Nlruka Sensei’s?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my intuition tells me\Nthat it’s positive…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, what are you two\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Let me make an introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tsubaki…\NMizuki’s fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiancée? Mizuki’s…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it’s negative…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s up with that reaction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki has caused problems\Nfor you again…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely apologize for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you know about\NMizuki’s prison break…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came by my house once…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became aware of that immediately\Nand tried to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But ultimately the result\Nwas that I allowed him to go…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really couldn’t be helped\Nin light of the situation…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I should have tried\Neven harder to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka, Naruto, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that I’m making\Nan impossible request!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to stop him,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki, I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, but I cannot allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can’t she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, we must hurry up\Nand search for Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she’s with us,\Nshe’ll interfere with our mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But… But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka… If that’s the case,\NI think I'll be of service to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea of\Nwhere he might be heading!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Tsubaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s probably no mistake…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it’s certain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he’ll use various tricks to camouflage\Nhis tracks as he flees…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we spend time on that…\Nit will all be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the matter of Nara No. 23…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what was the result?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ninja Herb: Creeping Saxifrage…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Who are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon, Rooster, Dog…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lookouts have been taken down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s an intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nara Clan’s research lab\Nwas attacked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… I just received a dispatch\Nfrom the Nara Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the dispatch,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the insurgent’s physical characteristics\Nmatch those of Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki’s…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that Naruto doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s something to have come up\Nwith the idea of the Nara Clan’s institute…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notwithstanding the abundance of\Nnarcotic substances that are stored there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,due to its remote mountain location,\Nsecurity is comparatively lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what substances were stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well… Because of their thorough control\Nof the substances,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were able to determine immediately\Nwhich substances were taken…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the description matched\Nafter all, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if a mere Chunin were\Nto remove those narcotic substances
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what would he be able\Nto do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… Thank you. You may go now…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\NI can’t take any chances…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing I can do if\NI don’t know what his objective is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can’t discern that from\Nthe actual materials…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there may still be some means…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the proportions\Nof the formula,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or possibly the order\Nin which they’re blended…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no mistake that\Nit’s this direction, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… Please continue to\Nproceed just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki, you said\N“It will all be too late.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you know what\Nhis objective is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably… Although maybe not totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki, please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, he told me…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will get my hands on Orochimaru’s power\Nand go to where Orochimaru is."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason he stole\Nthe Scroll of Sealing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was simply because\Nhe had chosen it as a hospitality gift…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki… You knew that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t convey it to the village…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just removing the Scroll of Sealing\Nis a serious felony…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover, I was scared for\Nwhat’d happen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if his real objective\Nhad come to light…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that he would\Nmend his ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case you cannot avoid\Nretribution either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am prepared for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you knew where Mizuki was going,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should have pursued him alone\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be able to stop him alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stop him at any cost…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want him to commit\Nany more crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Orochimaru…\NSo this was his plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, could an ordinary Ninja\Nreally manage to do this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s something only within
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the realm of an experienced\Nartisan’s technique…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a progress report on\Nthe inmate prison break incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right… Enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have just finished\Nrecapturing all inmates
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the exception of three –\NMizuki, Fujin and Raijin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are now continuing to investigate\Nthe other three…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:11:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the last inmate we captured said\Nsomething that concerned me…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that concerned you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… He apparently saw the three of\Nthem fleeing together…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujin and Raijin were fleeing\Nwith Mizuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tsunade…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no need for you to come…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If what he said is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the guys I sent out won’t be able\Nto deal with the situation alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shikamaru…\Nlf things continue like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we’ll be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re already in trouble…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru… All the Chakra is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve thought of several methods,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I let go of these guys we are\Ngonna find ourselves in trouble…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You insolent jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t take them down simply\Nby catching them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that’s why I’m doing this…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let you leave here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys have monstrous stamina…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what’s more,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,although their bodies\Nlook like rubber at first glance,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with that much muscle strength\Ntheir instantaneous reflexes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are probably quite something too…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you’re saying that this is\Nthe only possible method…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s do our best, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s no good…\Nlt’s unfortunate but, he can no longer…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…\NAll right! Let’s withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s unfortunate but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,guys who are of no use\Non the battleground
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only become a ball and chain…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it’s just a minor injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won’t be able to move\Nfrom this place, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Is it Genjutsu Paralysis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way… This can’t be, you’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are correct…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can’t be…\NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your whereabouts are supposed\Nto be unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t matter why…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I witnessed something\Nvery interesting earlier on…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took the life of\Nan injured comrade, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That piqued my interest…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not a sight one sees\Nvery often among the Leaf Shinobi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who devote their entire time\Nto playing house in the village…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t do anything wrong!\NI had no choice but to do what I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a short-tempered child,\Naren’t you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not reproaching you.\NYou were just carrying out your mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:15:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But… Is there anybody in\Nthe Leaf Village who acknowledges you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my present to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go visit that place if you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there hasn’t been\Na trespasser here before me…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eighth one on the right…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that power of\NOrochimaru’s anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don’t know when\Nhe encountered Orochimaru either…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I’m positive that the answer to\Nthose questions is waiting just up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Scroll of Sealing incident…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be angry about it,\Naren’t you, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:18:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t care about that in\Nthe least anymore…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I repaid my debt to that\Njerk Mizuki right there and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that guy is still connected\Nto Orochimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to ask him about something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there’s someone\NI need to find at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s up there…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this all…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will …
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will make me perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy has done something…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That smell gives me the shivers…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering who that was…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are really persistent,\Naren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is very convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was intending to take\Nyou guys down anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki… Your ambitions end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:20:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impudent as always, huh…\NHowever, you’re too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you always are…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful, don’t you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys…should feel honored\Nto be my first prey…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…almost like…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that’s they way it is,\Nisn’t it, Naruto…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true, you were actually special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru’s power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crappy news pass us by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you become speechless
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My voice is way too soft
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don’t answer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re crying   Crying alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?   I’m crying too
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Let my lonely scream ring out\Nthrough the night”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll thrash this confused era\Nwith my speed   Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’ll thrash this confused night\Nwith my speed   Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll thrash them with my piercing guitar\Nand my speed   Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sinking world and its evil bastards,\NI’ll kick their butt   Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what you meant by\Nthe “invincible body”?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much strength\Nyou gain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the kind of strength dependant\Non drugs can never be a true strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Just like Iruka Sensei says!\NOrochimaru’s Drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll crush that kind of nonsense,\Nso be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: “A Clash of Fate:\NYou Can’t Bring Me Down!”
